'''巨型麥哲倫望遠鏡'''（{{lang|en|'''Giant Magellan Telescope，GMT'''}}）是正在建造中，預計在2025年完工啟用的地基[[極大望遠鏡|極大望遠鏡]]<ref name="Amos2015">{{cite news |last=Amos |first=Jonathan |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-32984957 |title=Magellan super-scope gets green light for construction |work=BBC News |date=3 June 2015 |accessdate=2015-06-04 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112319/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-32984957 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，它包含7個直徑{{convert|8.4|m|ft|1|abbr=on}}的主鏡<ref name="GMTCastsNewMirror">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmto.org/newsitems/gmtfoldsphererelease2 |title=Giant Magellan Telescope Partner Institutions |accessdate=2007-04-03 |publisher=GMT Consortium |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070211070511/http://www.gmto.org/newsitems/gmtfoldsphererelease2 |archivedate=2007-02-11 |df= }}</ref>，將觀察可見光和近紅外線（320–25000 nm<ref name=requirements>{{Cite web |title=Giant Magellan Telescope Science Requirements |url=http://www.gmto.org/Resources/GMT-ID-01405-GMT_Science_Requirements.pdf |page=11 |accessdate=2008-03-31 |publisher=GMT Consortium}}</ref>），具有24.5米（80.4英尺）主鏡的解析能力，和相當於22.0米（72.2英尺）口徑的集光區域<ref>{{cite news |title=Giant telescope in race to become world's largest |date=2007-10-04 |author=Maggie McKee |publisher=[[New_Scientist|New Scientist]] |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn12742-giant-telescope-in-race-to-become-worlds-largest.html |accessdate=2007-10-07 |archive-date=2015-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503133728/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn12742-giant-telescope-in-race-to-become-worlds-largest.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這大約是368平方米（8.365米口徑的7倍）<ref name=design_optics/>。預期這架望遠鏡的解析度將是[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]的10倍，並且在其[[開光|開光]]使用時會是世界上最大的光學天台。在2015年12月，已經完成4面鏡子，而且山頂設施的建造工作也已經開始<ref name="Construction begins"/><ref name="pr-2015-11"/>。

計畫共使用7面鏡子，但開始運作時只會先使用其中的4面<ref name=hav>{{Cite web |url=http://harvardmagazine.com/2013/08/giant-magellan-milestone |title=Harvard Magazine - Giant Magellan Milestone (2013) |access-date=2019-03-19 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021053533/https://harvardmagazine.com/2013/08/giant-magellan-milestone |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Hutchins/>  這個價值10億美元的專案由美國主導，與澳大利亞、巴西和韓國合作，智利為地主國。

== 設置的場地 ==
[[File:Lco.jpg|thumb]]]]

望遠鏡的安裝地點是[[拉斯坎帕納斯天文台|拉斯坎帕納斯天文台]]<ref name="GMTOReport06">{{cite web |url=http://www.physorg.com/news110712104.html |title=Giant Magellan telescope site selected |publisher=Carnegie Institution |accessdate=2007-10-05 |archive-date=2012-03-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66N8Pa273?url=http://www.physorg.com/news110712104.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是[[麥哲倫望遠鏡|麥哲倫望遠鏡]]的所在地；位於[[智利|智利]][[拉塞雷納|拉塞雷納]]北北東約{{convert|115|km|mi|0|abbr=on}}和[[科皮亞波|科皮亞波]]南方 {{convert|180|km|mi|0|abbr=on}}，高度為{{convert|2516|m|ft|abbr=on}}<ref name=enclosure/><ref name=seeing/>。這個地點因為在一年中的大部分時間，以其出色的[[視寧度|視寧度]]和晴朗的天氣，已被選為新儀器的設置地點<ref name="TheBatt">{{cite news|url=http://media.www.thebatt.com/media/storage/paper657/news/2007/04/03/News/Eye-On.The.Sky-2819524.shtml |title=Eye on the sky |publisher=[[The_Battalion|The Battalion]] |accessdate=2007-04-03 |date=2007-04-03 |author=Robinson, Travis |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929105649/http://media.www.thebatt.com/media/storage/paper657/news/2007/04/03/News/Eye-On.The.Sky-2819524.shtml |archivedate=2007-09-29 |df= }}</ref>。此外，由於遠離人口聚集的中心和其它有利的地理條件：在[[亞他加馬沙漠|亞他加馬沙漠]]周圍大部分的地區，不僅沒有[[空氣汙染|空氣汙染]]，而且夜空受到[[光汙染#對天文學的影響|光汙染]]的影響也很小，使這一地區成為地球上長期天文觀測的最佳地點之一。主要地點的準備工作始於2012年3月23日，將山頂剷平的首次爆破。在2015年11月，於奠基儀式之後，現場開始施工<ref name="Construction begins">{{cite news |last=Amos |first=Jonathan |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-34791372 |title=Giant Magellan Telescope: Super-scope project breaks ground |work=BBC News |date=12 November 2015 |accessdate=2015-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128024104/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-34791372 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="pr-2015-11">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmto.org/2015/11/the-giant-magellan-telescope-organization-breaks-ground-in-chile/ |title=The Giant Magellan Telescope Organization Breaks Ground in Chile |access-date=2019-03-19 |archive-date=2018-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805083120/http://www.gmto.org/2015/11/the-giant-magellan-telescope-organization-breaks-ground-in-chile/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

