== 鏡片狀態 ==
總共有8片主鏡：一片中央主鏡片，6片離軸鏡片<ref name="gmto.org">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmto.org/SPIE_2012/8444-52.pdf |title=Giant Magellan Telescope - Overview |access-date=2019-03-20 |archive-date=2017-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110205449/http://www.gmto.org/SPIE_2012/8444-52.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，和一片備用的離軸鏡片<ref name="loft.optics.arizona.edu">{{cite conference |contribution=Status of mirror segment production for the Giant Magellan Telescope |first1=H. M. |last1=Martina |first2=J. H. |last2=Burgea |first3=J. M. |last3=Davisa |first4=D. W. |last4=Kimb |first5=J. S. |last5=Kingsleya |first6=K. |last6=Lawa |first7=A. |last7=Loeffa |first8=R. D. |last8=Lutza |first9=C. |last9=Merrilla |first10=P. A. |last10=Strittmattera |first11=M. T. |last11=Tuella |first12=S. N. |last12=Weinbergera |first13=S. C. |last13=Westa |contribution-url=http://www.loft.optics.arizona.edu/documents/journal_articles/GMT_SPIE_Buddy_2016.pdf |title=Advances in Optical and Mechanical Technologies for Telescopes and Instrumentation II |editor1-first=Ramón |editor1-last=Navarro |editor2-first=James H. |editor2-last=Burge |journal=Proc. SPIE |volume=9912 |page=99120V |conference=SPIE Astronomical Telescopes + Instrumentation |location=Edinburgh |conference-url=http://optics.org/events/2016/605 |date=22 July 2016 |doi=10.1117/12.2234491 |access-date=2019-03-20 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220140209/http://www.loft.optics.arizona.edu/documents/journal_articles/GMT_SPIE_Buddy_2016.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當鏡片被清洗和重新蒸鍍時，這些鏡片將會輪流來使用。這些反射鏡是使用下面有[[蜂窩結構|蜂窩結構]]的{{link-en|硼矽酸鹽玻璃|Borosilicate glass}}製成{{r|gmto.org}}；還為這架望遠鏡設計了調適光學的二次鏡{{r|gmto.org}}。望遠鏡開始觀測時只會使用4片鏡子：中央和周圍的3個離軸鏡片{{r|Hutchins}}。

